  "title": "Pale Formations",
  "description": "Eerie structures of unknown origin await deep within the Pale Garden. Who... rather, what, made these?",
  "body": "<center><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/sJcvkhDc/images/ffa7bc514f15281edf7e1b1462cabaef0d40c11e.png\" alt=\"Mysertious Ville\" width=\"600\"/></center>\n\n<hr>\n\nThe Pale Garden biome is inhabited. A variety of strange, mysterious structures lurk amongst the trees. \n\nIf you brush suspicious gravel around them, maybe you will discover answers.. especially at night. It seems the very forest around you rewards bravery...\n\n<center><img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/Xq1JfTc9/optimized.gif\" alt=\"GIF of loot changes at day/night\" width=\"500\"/></center>\n\n<hr>\n\n<center>Currently <strong>12</strong> structures, with <strong>26</strong> total unique variations. Check the <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/pale-formations/gallery\">gallery</a> for more examples.</center>\n\n<br>\n\n<center><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/sJcvkhDc/images/a5e0131c8034021c6221061b7ca2ce3e90dd2797.png\" alt=\"Waterhole\" width=\"600\"/></center>\n\n<hr>\n\n<center><a href=\"https://shop.purehosted.net/aff/wabi\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/089be7d8354008c5559afdaa2d957a9afb06f47d_0.webp\" alt=\"purehosted servers 10% coupon, pale formations custom\" width=\"600\"/></a></center>\n\n<hr>\n\n### Check out our other projects!\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/datapack/wabi-sabi-structures\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/db2c10d25e12c6023e03d3771113e2096cc82bd3.png\" alt=\"Wabi-Sabi Structures\" width=\"32\"/><strong> Wabi-Sabi Structures</strong></a>\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/datapack/revamped-shipwrecks\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/97f03f6580398b9e8014cce9a90ce4938f8d5451.png\" alt=\"Revamped Shipwrecks\" width=\"32\"/><strong> Revamped Shipwrecks</strong></a>\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/datapack/unwrecked-ships\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/222ee3a9b426b4cfaf8b967c0e